Geunyeoneun moleune nae ma-eum-eun
Babogat-i ajigdo geunyeol jabji maeil

[Verse 1: Simon Dominic]
Jeo nam-eun geulium-eul pihagin himdeulji
Aleungeolineun yeongsangdeul-eun miwojuggessjiman
Ajigdo nae gamjeong-eun tteugeowo teojil deus
Jam-eul jado geunyeo saeng-gag-e
Bupul-eo keojin kkum
Dol-awa jwo jebal
Museun mal-eul geuleohge hae
Naega geunyeol deo oelobge mandeun geos ttaem-e
Geunyeo ib-eseo geu hanmadiga naogi jeon
Muleup-ilado kkulhji mos haessdeon babo
Milyeonman nam-a
Mianhan ma-eum-e sigan-a dollyeojwo
Dasi geunyeowa michin deus-i
Datudeon geunal jeon-eulo
Jeojilseuleoun uisimgwa bulsunhan jibchag-eun
Nal huhoehage hane
Antakkaun i ma-eum-eun
Swibge ij-eul su eobs-eo geunyeol wihan sileul
Na jigeumdo eodum sog-eseo jeoggi bappeuji
Geu eotteon pyohyeon-eulodo
Geunyeol daesinhal su eobsji
Dasi gajil sun eobsjiman
Nae ma-eum-eun geunyeol baesinhal su eobs-euni

